<td colspan="2" class="fn summary" style="text-align:center; font-size: 125%; font-weight: bold; text-align:center; font-size:125%;"><b>Robert Falcon Scott</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding:4pt; line-height:1.25em; text-align:center; font-size:8pt;"><a href="/wiki/File:Robert_falcon_scott.jpg" class="image" title="Robert falcon scott.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/78/Robert_falcon_scott.jpg/200px-Robert_falcon_scott.jpg" width="200" height="216" border="0" /></a><br />
